{"tid":430584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會鄧家彪：慶祝辛亥革命106周年！","createTime":"2017-10-10T02:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T17:23:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8473dcb784b1f11fbb937a68c0886b50c73fd99a","tid":430584,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171010/s00001/26a4bdffab88607001e878d2a5c53b62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171010%2Fs00001%2F26a4bdffab88607001e878d2a5c53b62.jpg&h=7576cdb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日是10月10日，亦是辛亥革命106周年，加入了民建聯的工聯會前立法會議員鄧家彪，率先於facebook發帖慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪昨晚於facebook上載照片，顯示他出席了九龍巴士職工總會龍運巴士職工分會活動，並在印有國父孫中山、青天白日旗、以及寫上「慶祝第106周年辛亥革命 雙十節聯歡宴會」的背幕前合照。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪亦在fb留言「慶祝辛亥革命106周年！」"},{"pid":"2acb3e8e3d2becbd3d915d8d5524231899001226","tid":430584,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"好快就會被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家彪BB"},{"pid":"4b0b16f1550636c4a79831bec0876a97d004bc19","tid":430584,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"後面件國旗妹幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台妹？"},{"pid":"47b6965efdd1ccdd2295044f09d29f7541b1b7cc","tid":430584,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:59:24.000Z","msg":"暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d27a9f6b7c060476dccb6f757f3ef35ebb053b","tid":430584,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"唔知仲以為佢過檔勞聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96914066b12be86864a91d0f2e3fdc92d25187d4","tid":430584,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"